TypeDefinition

createhashmapobject [XPS_typ_ArgumentNilException, [_source*, _target*, _message*, _data*]]
Authors

Crashdome

Description

An exception for when an argument is nil and not expected to be.

Optionals
_source

(optional - Default: nil) - Anything

_target

(optional - Default: nil) - Anything

_message

(optional - Default: nil) - String - custom message to override the default

_data

(optional - Default: nil) - Hashmap - hashmap of data that provides more detail to cause of exception

Returns

HashmapObject
